OL,3,C'No guarantees' new hospital contract
OL,4,Cwill be signed before election
OL,6,FThere is "no guarantee" that Jersey's
OL,7,Fgovernment will sign a contract with
OL,8,Fthe company it chose to build the new
OL,9,F#710 million hospital before June's
OL,10,Felection, according to the Health
OL,11,FMinister.
OL,13,FDeputy Tom Binet told ITV News that
OL,14,Fwhile he hopes both parties will sign
OL,15,Fon the dotted line before the end of
OL,16,Fthis political term, it might not
OL,17,Fhappen.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1776456351
OL,3,C'No guarantees' new hospital contract
OL,4,Cwill be signed before election
OL,6,FThe Minister said: "While there's an
OL,7,Fawful lot of effort to see that we do
OL,8,Ftry and get this tidied up before the
OL,9,Fnext election, there's absolutely no
OL,10,Fguarantee, but that's what both sides
OL,11,Fare hoping to achieve."
OL,13,FLast summer, Deputy Binet told ITV
OL,14,FNews: "We're at what I'd called an
OL,15,Fadvanced and quite delicate stage.
OL,17,F"We want to have an appointment before
OL,18,Ftoo long. We're certainly looking to
OL,19,Fhave contracted work happening before
OL,20,Fthe next election which I think should
OL,21,Fput people's minds at rest."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1776456351
OL,3,C'No guarantees' new hospital contract
OL,4,Cwill be signed before election
OL,6,FAnd in November, the Government
OL,7,Fselected Bouygues UK as its preferred
OL,8,Fbidder to build the hospital at
OL,9,FOverdale.
OL,11,FAt that point, Deputy Binet said: "All
OL,12,Fof this progress gives me complete
OL,13,Fconfidence that the conditions are in
OL,14,Fplace for the Acute Hospital to be
OL,15,Funderway during the term of this
OL,16,FCouncil of Ministers, meeting our
OL,17,FCommon Strategic Priority commitment."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1776456351
OL,3,C'No guarantees' new hospital contract
OL,4,Cwill be signed before election
OL,6,FTwo years ago, the States approved the
OL,7,FCommon Strategic Policy, a list of 13
OL,8,Fpriorities decided on by the Council
OL,9,Fof Ministers, including the current
OL,10,FHealth Minister, to act on between
OL,11,F2024 and 2026.
OL,13,FOne of those goals was to 'deliver
OL,14,Furgent improvement in our health
OL,15,Fservices and begin construction of a
OL,16,Fnew hospital at Overdale.'
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1776456351
OL,3,C'No guarantees' new hospital contract
OL,4,Cwill be signed before election
OL,6,FHowever, despite the Minister saying
OL,7,Fplanning permission is now in place,
OL,8,Ffunding for it having been identified
OL,9,Fand development works now underway, a
OL,10,Fnew hospital still seems a long way
OL,11,Foff.
OL,13,FSince 2012, more than #204 million has
OL,14,Falready been spent on scrapped
OL,15,Fhospital plans and consultants' fees.
OL,17,FIn a statement, Deputy Binet says that
OL,18,Fministers remain "fully aligned" in
OL,19,Ftheir aim of building the new hospital.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1776456351
OL,3,C'No guarantees' new hospital contract
OL,4,Cwill be signed before election
OL,6,FHe said: "Our collective focus is on
OL,7,Fsecuring a robust agreement that
OL,8,Fdelivers the hospital as planned while
OL,9,Frepresenting appropriate value and
OL,10,Fprotection for the public purse.
OL,12,F"Ministers are united that decisions
OL,13,Fwill be taken in line with established
OL,14,Fguidance and codes of practice,
OL,15,Fincluding those that apply during the
OL,16,Felection period, should that be
OL,17,Fnecessary."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1776456351
OL,3,C'No guarantees' new hospital contract
OL,4,Cwill be signed before election
OL,6,FThe Minister added: "As with any live
OL,7,Fand confidential tender process, it is
OL,8,Fessential that commercial discussions
OL,9,Fare conducted carefully and
OL,10,Fresponsibly.
OL,12,F"As Minister for Health and Social
OL,13,FServices, I will complete this process
OL,14,Fonly when satisfied that the terms
OL,15,Fdeliver a fair, balanced and
OL,16,Fsustainable agreement in the best
OL,17,Finterests of both parties, but
OL,18,Fespecially islanders."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
